ITT Educational Services, Inc., et al.
Debtor Website






Chapter 7  Case No. 16-07207U.S. Bankruptcy Court - Southern District of IndianaHon. James M. Carr




Welcome Creditors
On September 16, 2016 (the "Petition Date"), ITT Educational Services, Inc., ESI Service Corp., and Daniel Webster College, Inc. (the "Debtors") filed petitions in the United States Bankruptcy Court for the Southern District of Indiana seeking relief under the provisions of Chapter 7 of the United States Bankruptcy Code.
Telephonic inquiries can be made at: (888) 857-4008

Please contact the Court before hearings if appearing telephonically. The Court has requested that any parties attending telephonically notify the court beforehand so they can note their name and who they represent.  Parties should contact the following:
heather_butler@insb.uscourts.gov 317-229-3833
suzette_bewley@insb.uscourts.gov 317-229-3862

 
